ygData.messageBody:
Hi all! I'm new to RPGs in general but I'm having
lots of fun playing Everquest. I'm a 9th lvl female
woodelf on the Bristlebane server named Bebinn. How many
female rangers are there? <br>I was doing good, just got
my spells, had much armor and a good amount of money
(not a whole lot, i don't go around begging) when I
died AGAIN!!!!!. Gawd, this game is frustrating. I
love it tho, my whole family is addicted.<br>Anybody
have any good advice? Where to go, where not to go? I
don't group up much so I need some advice about things
I can do by myself. Any info on quests would be
greatly appreciated. <br>Look me up on Bristlebane
<br><br>Bebinn
